{
  "video_id": "_r0VX-aU_T8",
  "title": "The Design Thinking Process",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 3280.0,
      "text": "Design Thinking is a 5-step process to come up with"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3280.0,
      "end_time": 5880.0,
      "text": "meaningful ideas that solve real problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5880.0,
      "end_time": 8200.0,
      "text": "for a particular group of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8400.0,
      "end_time": 10760.0,
      "text": "The process is taught in top design"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10760.0,
      "end_time": 12940.0,
      "text": "and business schools around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 12940.0,
      "end_time": 16120.0,
      "text": "It has brought many businesses lots of happy customers"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 16120.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18740.0,
      "text": "and helped entrepreneurs from all around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 18740.0,
      "end_time": 22360.0,
      "text": "to solve problems with innovative new solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 24420.0,
      "end_time": 26920.0,
      "text": "Step 1: Empathize"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 27160.0,
      "end_time": 30040.0,
      "text": "The purpose of step one is to conduct interviews"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 30040.0,
      "end_time": 31440.0,
      "text": "that give you an idea about"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 31440.0,
      "end_time": 33760.0,
      "text": "what people really care about."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 33760.0,
      "end_time": 36460.0,
      "text": "We need to empathize with their situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 36460.0,
      "end_time": 39460.0,
      "text": "For example, if you want to help old people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 39460.0,
      "end_time": 41040.0,
      "text": "you might find that they want to keep"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 41040.0,
      "end_time": 43020.0,
      "text": "the ability to walk around."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 43020.0,
      "end_time": 47780.0,
      "text": "In your conversations, they might share with you different ways they can do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 47780.0,
      "end_time": 51080.0,
      "text": "Later into the interview you'll want to dig a little deeper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51080.0,
      "end_time": 52580.0,
      "text": "look for personal stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 52580.0,
      "end_time": 55540.0,
      "text": "or situations where things became difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 55540.0,
      "end_time": 58340.0,
      "text": "Ideally, you redo the process with many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 58340.0,
      "end_time": 60460.0,
      "text": "with the same problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 61780.0,
      "end_time": 64500.0,
      "text": "Step 2: Define the Problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 64500.0,
      "end_time": 67520.0,
      "text": "Looking at the interviews, you can now understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 67520.0,
      "end_time": 71800.0,
      "text": "the actual needs that people are trying to fulfill with certain activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 72160.0,
      "end_time": 74780.0,
      "text": "One way to do that is to underline the verbs"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 74780.0,
      "end_time": 76780.0,
      "text": "or activities that the people mentioned"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 76780.0,
      "end_time": 78540.0,
      "text": "when talking about their problems:"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78540.0,
      "end_time": 82160.0,
      "text": "like going for a walk, meeting old friends for tea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82160.0,
      "end_time": 85500.0,
      "text": "or simply going grocery shopping around the corner store."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 85740.0,
      "end_time": 88840.0,
      "text": "You might realize it's not so much about going out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88840.0,
      "end_time": 91220.0,
      "text": "but more about staying in touch."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 91400.0,
      "end_time": 95180.0,
      "text": "After your analysis, formulate a problem statement:"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 95340.0,
      "end_time": 97840.0,
      "text": "“Some elderly are afraid to be lonely."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97840.0,
      "end_time": 99960.0,
      "text": "They want to stay connected.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 101620.0,
      "end_time": 104420.0,
      "text": "Step 3: Ideate"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 104420.0,
      "end_time": 107120.0,
      "text": "Now focus only on the problem statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 107120.0,
      "end_time": 109880.0,
      "text": "and come up with ideas that solve the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 110180.0,
      "end_time": 112800.0,
      "text": "The point is not to get a perfect idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 112800.0,
      "end_time": 115080.0,
      "text": "but rather to come up with as many ideas:"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 115080.0,
      "end_time": 118180.0,
      "text": "like unique virtual reality experiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 118180.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "senior friendly hover boards or a modified pushcart."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 122500.0,
      "end_time": 125600.0,
      "text": "Whatever it is, sketch up your best ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 125600.0,
      "end_time": 128020.0,
      "text": "and show them to the people you are trying to help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 128020.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130380.00000000001,
      "text": "so you get their feedback."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 131680.0,
      "end_time": 134180.0,
      "text": "Step 4: Prototype"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 134440.0,
      "end_time": 137440.0,
      "text": "Now take a moment to reflect on what you have learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 137440.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "from your conversations about the different ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 140440.0,
      "end_time": 143000.0,
      "text": "Ask yourself, how does your idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 143000.0,
      "end_time": 145920.0,
      "text": "fit in the context of people's actual lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 146160.0,
      "end_time": 149220.0,
      "text": "Your solution could be a combination of a new idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 149220.0,
      "end_time": 151400.0,
      "text": "and what is already being used."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 151400.0,
      "end_time": 155040.0,
      "text": "Then connect the dots, sketch up your final solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 155040.0,
      "end_time": 157100.0,
      "text": "and go build a real prototype"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 157100.0,
      "end_time": 159540.0,
      "text": "that's just good enough to be tested."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 161240.0,
      "end_time": 163480.0,
      "text": "Step 5: Test"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 164000.0,
      "end_time": 167400.0,
      "text": "Now test your prototype with actual users."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 167400.0,
      "end_time": 170740.0,
      "text": "Don't defend your idea in case people don't like it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 170740.0,
      "end_time": 173680.0,
      "text": "the point is to learn what works and what didn't,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 173680.0,
      "end_time": 175800.0,
      "text": "so any feedback is great."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 175800.0,
      "end_time": 178860.0,
      "text": "Then go back to ideation or prototyping"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 178860.0,
      "end_time": 180460.0,
      "text": "and apply your learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 180800.0,
      "end_time": 183240.0,
      "text": "Repeat the process until you have a prototype"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 183240.0,
      "end_time": 185980.0,
      "text": "that works and solves the real problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 186340.0,
      "end_time": 190340.0,
      "text": "Now you are ready to change the world or open shop."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 191660.0,
      "end_time": 194860.0,
      "text": "To experience design thinking first hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 194860.0,
      "end_time": 198040.0,
      "text": "do the free virtual design thinking crash course"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 198040.0,
      "end_time": 200510.0,
      "text": "from Stanford's D-School right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 200510.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "You will learn to design a new gift giving experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 204580.0,
